phrases: Bell-kun, are we at that town yet?
Just a little more, I think, Goddess.
This was supposed to be a date for just you and me, Bell-kun...
So what are all those people doing here?
The monsters visit this floor just as we do.
It would be more appropriate to call this
the monsters' paradise, instead of ours.
Goddess, this world is beautiful, is not it?
Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon?
It is a town founded by adventurers.
This beat-up old bag is 20,000 valis?
If you do not want to buy, that does not bother me.
The inns here are absurdly expensive, too.
That is why we camp in the forest.
It is that rookie kid from the bar!
You are going to pay for what happened back there
I knew you would say that.
You bought something like that here?
You do not know how to spend money.
You bought that backpack, did not you?
We need this to get back to the surface!
I did not have a choice!
And I need my perfume, too!
Bell-kun, you do not like sweaty girls, do you?
I have never thought about that.
Hestia-sama, we are all going to take a bath after this.
We would like to come, too!
Bell-kun, once we get back to camp, can I have a little of your time?
Hauling antidotes is a pain, do not make me do
Thanks to you, we can leave for the surface in the morning.
We will be splitting into two groups,
and you should go with the first
What is the bunny brat doing here?
What do you mean, some stuff?
I followed you here because you said you wanted to speak alone.
But why are we climbing a tree?
You will understand if you follow.
Why are you comparing yourself to the others, Hestia-sama?
Obviously, we are going to peek.
That is not obvious at all!
Bell-kun, peeking is part of a man's romance.
Bell, peeking is part of a man's romance.
What, did you come to take a bath, too?
I had you pegged as the quiet type.
Oh, Bell-kun, you are so silly.
There is no need to worry about it.
Y-You are going to forgive me?
You do not think I am lying?
It is a bad habit of yours.
It is a little late for this,
but thanks for coming all this way to save me.
I was planning on coming here sometime soon, anyway.
Mama Mia gives me time off, every so often, to bring them flowers.
It is the grave of the familia I belonged to once.
An enemy familia set a trap for us in the dungeon,
and everyone but me was killed.
would you listen to my story?
I am blacklisted from the guild.
I wiped out that enemy familia.
Driven by rage, I avenged my comrades, doing whatever was necessary.
And when I would had my revenge,
I collapsed in a dark, abandoned alleyway.
It would have been a fitting end for one who behaved so stupidly.
So you work at the Benevolent Mistress now?
Mama Mia knew everything, and yet she still took me in.
I am sorry to tell you such an awful tale.
I am a shameless, violent elf.
Enough so that I might betray your trust.
You are a human worthy of my respect.
Wow, you are pissed off, Moldo!
What trick did that brat use to get down here?
A bratty little rookie got down here practically the day he leveled up.
We have been here for years, which means we are a joke!
We will just have to teach him that.
If we can just get him alone...
You got to do something even I cannot, you bastard!
We blamed the whole thing on Hermes-sama.
Let me go, you stupid amazon!
What is he doing here, anyway?
I have been assigned to the party that is leaving first.
You are going with the second party, right?
If he wanted to peek, he should have come when I was alone!
come to the lone, tall crystal on the far east side of the central forest.
Do you really think you can get away with this?
I may not look like it, but I am a goddess!
I am not shameless enough to hurt her.
Then you are here for me.
I will not let them interfere.
We are about to have a fight.
The winner can tell the loser to do whatever he wants.
If I win, I am taking all your equipment.
If I win, please release my goddess.
But do not get the wrong idea, brat.
In this show, I am going to kick the crap out of you!
Snap the Rookie brat in half!
It is too early for your nap!
You are the Rookie all eyes are on, huh?
Do you have something against Bell Cranel?
You could say this is my love.
Bell-kun does not know enough about the ugly side of humanity.
Nasty or not, I wanted him to learn this about people.
I will not deny that part of it is the entertainment, though.
And if his fangs are broken here?
That means he was never right for the job.
Looks like they have found out, too.
They are all so dazzlingly bright...
Bell should be just past them!
It is the Little Rookie's buddies!
Sounds like they are having fun.
Damn it, I want to go see!
I used my chienthrope sense of smell.
It is thanks to the perfume you wasted your money on.
We cannot get close to Bell!
It seems you have not learned your lesson.
I can feel his eyes on me.
I will chop you in half, asshole!
I guess our fun for the day is over!
Bell-kun, I am so glad you are safe!
I am sorry you got beaten up so badly over me...
No, I am sorry that I could not protect you.
I do not like this shaking.
Hey, what the hell is that?
Familia Myth The Story of a Familia
